These scripts are used to install Atmosphere and it's dependencies.

  sudo source atmo.sh

to install Atmosphere and all it's dependencies.


+ atmo.sh

  - distro.sh

    Provide information on the distro.

  - euca2ools.sh

    Install euca2ools.

  - faye.sh

    Install and configure faye.

  - getOpts.sh

    Provide and handle options.

  - packages.sh

    Install required packages.

  - py.sh

    Install and configure python and any python dependencies.

  - postgres.sh

    Install and configure postgres database for atmosphere.

  - nodejs.sh

    Install and configure nodejs and npm.

